title: unicode-property-aliases-ecmascript [![Build status](https://travis-ci.org/mathiasbynens/unicode-property-aliases-ecmascript.svg?branch=master)](https://travis-ci.org/mathiasbynens/unicode-property-aliases-ecmascript)
description: unicode-property-aliases-ecmascript offers Unicode property alias mappings in an easy-to-consume JavaScript format. It only contains the Unicode property names that are supported in ECMAScript RegExp property escapes.
